## Project conventions ‚Äî read first

The rules live in `{{ ai_folder }}/instructions/`. Start from the README
index in each relevant folder; it is a table of contents that says which
detail file covers what. **Load detail files on demand** ‚Äî when the task
touches that area ‚Äî rather than reading the whole tree up front. The
instruction files are authoritative: if this file conflicts, they win.

