## Working style

{% if use_spec_kit %}- **Features start with a spec** (SDD): spec ‚Üí plan ‚Üí tasks, then implement. See `general/sdd.md`; `just sdd-init` installs spec-kit.
{% endif %}- **Micro-implementation is test-driven** (red-green-refactor). See `general/tdd.md`.
- **Design is DDD**: ubiquitous language, layering, pure domain. See `general/ddd.md`.
{% if 'python' in languages %}- **Python runs through `uv`** ‚Äî never `python`, `pip`, `poetry`, `virtualenv` directly. Always `uv run ...`, `uv add ...`. See `python/tooling.md`.
{% endif %}- **Skills** in `{{ ai_folder }}/skills/`: `tdd-cycle`, `design-review`, `refactor-code-smell`, `lint-and-format`, `run-tests`{% if 'python' in languages %}, `python-uv-setup`{% endif %}.
- **Subagents** in `{{ ai_folder }}/agents/`: `code-reviewer`, `ddd-architect`, `tdd-driver`{% if 'python' in languages %}, `python-refactorer`{% endif %}.

## Source layout

```
src/application/      Use cases, services, orchestration
src/domain/           Pure business logic (entities, value objects, interfaces)
src/infrastructure/   DB, network, drivers, external adapters
src/presentation/     Entry points (HTTP routers, CLI, ISRs)
tests/{unit,integration,e2e,performance}
```

Each layer ships with a `README.md` explaining what belongs inside. The
canonical home of every artifact is the "Where things live" table in
`{{ ai_folder }}/instructions/general/architecture.md`. Do not create
new top-level folders.

